Class Summary
Arena Arena - The first (and perhaps the only) stage for Snake.

ReplayThread ReplayThread - Thread that allows a game of snake to start itself over from the beginning.
Score Score - A simple class designed for storing high scores
ScoreKeeper ScoreKeeper - saves scores
ScoreQueue ScoreQueue - A simple max heap for storing high scores and names
Snake Snake - A representation of a snake consisting of a queue of coordinates
